

---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="brain fog? here’s how to fix it naturally"
  description="if your mind feels slow, cloudy, or unfocused, learn what causes brain fog and how to clear it naturally."
>
  <section class="page-hero section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <p class="eyebrow">guide</p>
      <h1>brain fog? here’s what’s causing it</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        if your mind feels slow, cloudy, or hard to focus, it’s usually a sign your system is overloaded or out of rhythm.
      </p>
      <p class="lead">
        fix the inputs, and mental clarity starts to return.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>common causes</h2>
        <div class="content-list">
          <p>poor sleep quality</p>
          <p>too much screen time</p>
          <p>lack of morning sunlight</p>
          <p>low physical movement</p>
          <p>poor diet and hydration</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>what’s happening</h2>
        <p>
          your brain runs on rhythm. when sleep, light, movement, and stimulation are out of sync,
          cognitive speed and clarity naturally drop.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section accent-section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <h2>quick reset</h2>
      <div class="content-block">
        <p>get morning sunlight within 1 hour of waking</p>
        <p>reduce late-night screen exposure</p>
        <p>walk daily to increase circulation</p>
        <p>sleep at consistent times</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <div class="y2k-panel feature-card">
        <div class="panel-heading-row">
          <p class="panel-kicker">optional tool</p>
          <span class="panel-stamp">clarity</span>
        </div>
        <h2>reduce stimulation</h2>
        <p>
          blue light blocking glasses can help reduce overstimulation from screens and support clearer thinking.
        </p>
        <a href="/recommendations/blue-light-glasses" class="button">view recommended option</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <div class="y2k-panel feature-card">
        <div class="panel-heading-row">
          <p class="panel-kicker">optional tool</p>
          <span class="panel-stamp">nervous system</span>
        </div>
        <h2>support calm focus</h2>
        <p>
          magnesium can help support nervous system balance, which can improve mental clarity over time.
        </p>
        <a href="/recommendations/magnesium" class="button">view recommended option</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <div class="y2k-panel feature-card">
        <div class="panel-heading-row">
          <p class="panel-kicker">related</p>
          <span class="panel-stamp">system</span>
        </div>
        <h2>go deeper</h2>
        <div class="content-list">
          <p><a href="/cant-focus">fix focus issues</a></p>
          <p><a href="/low-motivation">restore motivation</a></p>
          <p><a href="/how-to-fix-sleep">fix sleep first</a></p>
          <p><a href="/start-here">understand the full system</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>